To build docs:
Install sphinx RTD theme and argparse packages
    conda install sphinx_rtd_theme
    conda install sphinx-argparse
In the docs folder run
    make html
To remove existing docs and start with a fresh build environment run
    make clean
    Then
    make html

The generated html pages will be in docs/_build/html.  Open docs/_build/html/index.html with a browser to view
the documentation.
